**Issue:** All endpoints accept unlimited requests. This enables credential stuffing, scraping, and resource exhaustion.

**Fix:** Use [express-rate-limit](https://github.com/express-rate-limit/express-rate-limit):

```bash
npm install express-rate-limit
```

```js
